The Boys from Brazil is a 1978 British-American science fiction thriller film directed by Franklin J. Schaffner .
It stars Gregory Peck and Laurence Olivier and features James Mason , Lilli Palmer , Uta Hagen , Denholm Elliott , and Steve Guttenberg in supporting roles .
The film is based on the 1976 novel of the same name by Ira Levin , and was nominated for three Academy Awards .